Code to convert HB matrices to hypergraph and graph files readable by Zoltan,
and to measure communication volume of matrix-vector multiplication with a 
given decomposition of a HB matrix.

Files:
  hb_to_hg.c     -- converts HB to zdrive-formatted hypergraph.
  hb_to_graph.c  -- converts HB to graph.
  hb_to_hmetis.c -- converts HB to hMETIS-formatted hypergraph.
  hb_print.c     -- displays an HB matrix.
  metric.c     -- measure communication volume of matrix-vector multiplication.
  Other *.c    -- Matrix Market code for reading a HB matrix file.

Documentation on usage of metric.c is included in comments in metric.c.

